Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11回了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11是素數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是素數
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素數的定義是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了1和那個數本身之外沒有其它因數的1以外的正整數
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡素了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修飾過多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  非素數的定義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是素數的正整數
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒化妝呢
