Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PUZZLE很狡猾  謎題很可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  翼與貓  其二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.36,0:24:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼  假數的定義是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
